Package: omnishell
Section: x11
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libomnishell1 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Desktop-like shell environment in a single application
 OmniShell provides a Windows-style desktop environment implemented as a
 single wxWidgets application. It offers a desktop, taskbar, start menu,
 system tray and a modular application system backed by a virtual file
 system abstraction layer.

Package: libomnishell1
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: shared library for OmniShell desktop environment
 This package contains the shared library used by OmniShell-based
 applications. It provides core module infrastructure, shell integration
 helpers and common UI/runtime functionality.

Package: libomnishell-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libomnishell1 (= ${binary:Version}), libboost-dev, libhowardhinnant-date-dev, ${misc:Depends}
Description: development files for OmniShell desktop environment
 This package contains the development headers, pkg-config file and
 unversioned shared library symlink needed to build applications and
 services against libomnishell.
